if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a397f04ab089704154d0b25cedaa54493e2f556","tid":255854,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:46:43.000Z","msg":"我除咗講恭喜之外，都唔知應該講乜嘢好"},{"pid":"785f3989e2ef4e1f7965791d57725680116712ad","tid":255854,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Backup完iCloud既相 好似只會保留30日<br />\n<br />\n因為我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下<br />\n<br />\n我個icloud 圖庫keep 住有backup 架喎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/154929_1523add988e8e8e95dd6440fbcb3f0a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F154929_1523add988e8e8e95dd6440fbcb3f0a3.jpg&h=a8a39508&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2a1d50867c7d724b60c87a193d937cbcf1e033c","tid":255854,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:50:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a0c0ee1876901448f81c28eb4b3b4cea619ff5b","tid":255854,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f46e1a3953b351b31c82b9f9e541b174b0e97e7","tid":255854,"uid":1156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>再次restore from backup</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一直都係用icloud backup<br />\n<br />\n冇用itunes 好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n琴晚都係正常下載及安裝（冇連pc)<br />\n<br />\n咁我依家唯有洗機，再backup from icloud 試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n同埋我琴晚九點左右完成update<br />\n<br />\n半夜（平時）icloud 會自動backup<br />\n<br />\n呢個時間性有冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾千張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用 update 前ok 的 backup"},{"pid":"af8bfe238ce719636b771cc7382751b713a3b89d","tid":255854,"uid":1156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:56:59.000Z","msg":"手機 files 唔齊再 backup 的話...... 劣幣驅逐良幣"},{"pid":"98ccb00d914baf97c99686698f48351225210b12","tid":255854,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/155905_22e7ddb74ff33396ba20aa0c049b0944.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F155905_22e7ddb74ff33396ba20aa0c049b0944.jpg&h=610de74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解琴晚升完ios10冇backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即係我晏d 返去重置再backup from icloud 就得啦（正常情況下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n依家我係咪要熜左icloud 自動backup 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed007738c25780e246a9f3084d20930bfbc3cfe","tid":255854,"uid":65088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:01:23.000Z","msg":"iOS8升10.3 反而多咗相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前完全del左果d<br />\n唔知點解係番刪除相片果度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b476ea0bf53982ba87633b2e17d0ddc4abc6b220","tid":255854,"uid":1156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/24/155905_22e7ddb74ff33396ba20aa0c049b0944.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F24%2F155905_22e7ddb74ff33396ba20aa0c049b0944.jpg&h=610de74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解琴晚升完ios10冇backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即係我晏d 返去重置再backup from icloud 就得啦（正常情況下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n依家我係咪要熜左icloud 自動backup 先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好像最安全"},{"pid":"e9119d35b0d928c0357f2abaa51bea4da7c7946a","tid":255854,"uid":1156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:03:29.000Z","msg":"Anyway, 希望你最後無事"},{"pid":"e98814baf1ad06ae333512a3f7b627f124a58b10","tid":255854,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:03:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>iOS8升10.3 反而多咗相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前完全del左果d<br />\n唔知點解係番刪除相片果度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點撚解呀喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9416efbd827d7ecc431b3d3957209fea6437c9","tid":255854,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Anyway, 希望你最後無事</blockquote><br />\n謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我熜左自動backup 先<br />\n<br />\n跟住返屋企連wifi logout 再login 個icloud.睇下sync 唔sync 得返d 相（apple 教）<br />\n<br />\n唔得就重置再backup from icloud<br />\n<br />\n以上做法我都唔會連電腦（ok嗎）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e05442430923f632951975a251a8c745236227","tid":255854,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa99544db2de8029d8fadd9fc09dd2f04ca635a0","tid":255854,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236162d88d9b442760f7decbab487b0b6750aedc","tid":255854,"uid":1156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Anyway, 希望你最後無事</blockquote><br />\n謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我熜左自動backup 先<br />\n<br />\n跟住返屋企連wifi logout 再login 個icloud.睇下sync 唔sync 得返d 相（apple 教）<br />\n<br />\n唔得就重置再backup from icloud<br />\n<br />\n以上做法我都唔會連電腦（ok嗎）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得直接 清機 restore, then restore from iCloud backup<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（唔等唔費時，你等icloud download photos through wifi 都可能幾個鐘先知道得還是唔得)"},{"pid":"c46c16c0090c2e2e2c2c3136059cd3058c751f5b","tid":255854,"uid":2628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:09:19.000Z","msg":"用開google photo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fee443cf216f328c2d754cc8eb5aee9c053cbc9","tid":255854,"uid":18573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:15:23.000Z","msg":"個iCloud Drive係用嚟放文件嗰啲 同埋同mac機桌面同步<br />\n相要去返相片/Photo App到睇 <br />\n如果login多次未即刻見到試下差住電連wifi放佢一晚係到睇下點"},{"pid":"a1cc5c331d387eb8bab6a53763cd8dd94e6d42bd","tid":255854,"uid":18573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:16:47.000Z","msg":"之後都建議開返個Auto Backup啦因為有咩事上嚟都可以有個backup"},{"pid":"7b7bec8b1b3b54e89c7ef445fed71cebb95839fe","tid":255854,"uid":18573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個iCloud Drive係用嚟放文件嗰啲 同埋同mac機桌面同步<br />\n相要去返相片/Photo App到睇 <br />\n如果login多次未即刻見到試下差住電連wifi放佢一晚係到睇下點</blockquote><br />\n因為唔知點解iCloud down相係幾慢下... <br />\n平時啲舊相唔係機到係iCloud到開嚟睇都要等陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1ecafe1591fe976317a33cb3dff5b5bee6e7a5","tid":255854,"uid":62658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:18:33.000Z","msg":"都係過落電腦或者google photo 安全，又唔洗個個月課金"},{"pid":"fd26447198b4fff9cca3b66007d3eb71ff7f50f4","tid":255854,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係過落電腦或者google photo 安全，又唔洗個個月課金</blockquote><br />\n唉<br />\n<br />\n之前一直都有用pc backup,唔知幾時開始一連電腦backup 就斷線，所以先買icloud"},{"pid":"c3c6d718d695723603cda214a9f6d3189f06d578","tid":255854,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個iCloud Drive係用嚟放文件嗰啲 同埋同mac機桌面同步<br />\n相要去返相片/Photo App到睇 <br />\n如果login多次未即刻見到試下差住電連wifi放佢一晚係到睇下點</blockquote><br />\n相片/photo app 即係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好既我會試下，但其實琴晚更新完都已經連住wifi (同平時一樣），但唔知點解冇backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abd053a0452cc62e6b2376c04b2d2826c8ec4bc","tid":255854,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:38:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之後都建議開返個Auto Backup啦因為有咩事上嚟都可以有個backup</blockquote><br />\n我最後果次backup 係更新前（仲keep 住幾千張相）<br />\n<br />\n我驚開左auto backup 會覆蓋左琴日有幾千張相個save<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋我icloud 開左呢個icloud 圖片庫（另外斬一舊相片）出黎，有冇關係，其實唔知有乜分別點解會分多一part 出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4cd8dfe443ce0d764747ff33f70abca97e1d568","tid":255854,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Anyway, 希望你最後無事</blockquote><br />\n謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我熜左自動backup 先<br />\n<br />\n跟住返屋企連wifi logout 再login 個icloud.睇下sync 唔sync 得返d 相（apple 教）<br />\n<br />\n唔得就重置再backup from icloud<br />\n<br />\n以上做法我都唔會連電腦（ok嗎）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得直接 清機 restore, then restore from iCloud backup<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（唔等唔費時，你等icloud download photos through wifi 都可能幾個鐘先知道得還是唔得)</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94841c7f146af2937fa754776b8285d3b6f459a8","tid":255854,"uid":68632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:42:22.000Z","msg":"Make sure the iCloud Photo Library has been enabled. Connect with a stable wifi network and plug to power, wait, done"}]}